{"tid":1046512,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"懷舊校服，有誰穿過","createTime":"2019-03-04T10:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T11:01:26.000Z","uid":235650,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53cc3078ac2a6bf31891d9a80a55a7a78891eeff","tid":1046512,"uid":235650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"公司附近有一家校服公司。<br />\n今天經過，看到門口有一件特價衣服。<br />\n很熟眼，但想不起來。<br />\n進去問老闆，原來是以前的體育服，印個校章在胸前，就是一個鮮蹦活跳的期待。<br />\n不過已經沒有學校選擇這款老土的體育服，所以特價清貨。<br />\n我買下一件當瞓覺衫着，希望能做個愉快的小學夢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/175926_d1fae52d33a4dca4e92ba0ae6d3a2aca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F175926_d1fae52d33a4dca4e92ba0ae6d3a2aca.png&h=502113fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/175935_1771559db634ddfd6e61d1c80f2111b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F175935_1771559db634ddfd6e61d1c80f2111b7.png&h=a1591e23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83890b579c6b4681cd1076af1f865eaf84f2a3bc","tid":1046512,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb3752492d3c4fcd6394b547c737c300d44e9a8d","tid":1046512,"uid":235650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"搭巴士成日經過"}]}